---
title: Flamegrilled Smokey Beef & Avocado Burger with Buttered Corn Cob
description: This burger means business! Fire up the grill and grab your BBQ tongs, tonight’s handheld meal features a smokey-spiced beef
patty, avocado and crisp salad leaves on a warm toasty bun. Paired with a buttery, golden corn cob, it’s the ultimate backyard
feast—no invite required!
